{"tid":146961,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"諗起5年前既趣事。想同巴打們分享下。","createTime":"2017-03-07T13:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T15:13:04.000Z","uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9d62643663f240d5f072f6abda7aafec1b515f","tid":146961,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:43:32.000Z","msg":"話說&hellip; 半年前我個朋友去麥當勞，叫了一個普通餐。吃完之後覺得不夠飽，就跑去旁邊潮州打冷鋪頭叫外賣，誰不知撞到舊同學都響度 <br />\n於是就坐低邊食邊隊啤。飲到面紅耳熱，上去其中一個同學屋企鋤D，輸左舊零水。我個朋友條氣唔順，想話去出出火。 <br />\n0甘橋有新女番，二話不説除衫上牀，誰不知未曾真崮就撞正差人掃黃。拉左番差舘協助調查。搞到要女朋友黎接。 <br />\n唔接由自可，女友返到屋企就執野，好決絕0甘話分手。 <br />\n於是我個朋友到而家都仲要孤家寡人。 <br />\n上次見到，好真誠0甘告誡我:&quot;記住下次食麥記，一定一定一定，要加大。&quot;"},{"pid":"998b158d7cd66ca90c4e9e5a71ea8f6a4ace145f","tid":146961,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:45:19.000Z","msg":"食boa米算 抵拒死拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429fb67a9ae215788c5c8c327ea946ecb4e83a8a","tid":146961,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be675bd6caec2465275ab71299f5a3219b6e5e5","tid":146961,"uid":18663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:30:18.000Z","msg":"唔好笑"},{"pid":"00659f0da0c0d998643675c4949706ec9175eefe","tid":146961,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:31:57.000Z","msg":"0甘"},{"pid":"98d1ba64ec8c20baaf59bbbb6d9b67074b424134","tid":146961,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:33:58.000Z","msg":"喂呀哥，比D誠意呀，又半年又5年，改下唔係好難姐"},{"pid":"04f8ab44c1f000ebf0e38ee97ea68250db9d395d","tid":146961,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:40:14.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28823bd504d8226484c134e51c307208036747d2","tid":146961,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc